# Battle of SPS 🎮

A Python implementation of the classic Rock-Paper-Scissors game.

## Features
- Play against the computer
- Random computer choices
- Win/Lose/Tie detection
- Beginner-friendly Python project

## Technologies Used
- Python 3
- random module

## How to Run

python Rock_Paper_Scissors.py

